The notice required by § 8-401 of this subtitle shall be served on the owner or other appropriate person:
by leaving a copy of the notice at the person's residence;
by sending a copy of the notice by United States mail to the mailing address of the owner;
by personal service by the sheriff in the same manner as original service is required in a civil action; or
